sequenceDiagram
  actor C as Caller
  participant FE1 as Caller CallModal
  participant WS as Socket.IO Backend
  participant DB as MongoDB
  participant FE2 as Callee

  rect rgb(235, 245, 255)
    Note over C,FE2: Call Invite + Signaling
    C->>FE1: Start audio/video call
    FE1->>FE1: getUserMedia + create offer
    FE1->>WS: emit call:invite(calleeId, offer)
    WS->>DB: Create Call(status=ringing)
    DB-->>WS: callId
    WS-->>FE2: emit call:invite
    FE2->>WS: emit call:signal(answer/ICE)
    WS-->>FE1: forward call:signal
    FE1->>WS: emit call:end
    WS->>DB: Update Call status ended/missed
    WS-->>FE2: emit call:ended
  end

  rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
    Note over C,FE2: Linked Devices / Session Revoke
    FE1->>WS: HTTP GET /auth/sessions
    WS->>DB: Find Session documents for user
    DB-->>WS: sessions[]
    WS-->>FE1: sessions list
    FE1->>WS: HTTP DELETE /auth/sessions/:sessionId
    WS->>DB: Set revokedAt and revokedReason
    WS-->>FE1: ok
  end
